{"tid":1611813,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【黑色10.1】龍翔道開槍片段曝光 便裝警實彈射幾十米外抗爭者","createTime":"2019-10-02T05:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T06:13:56.000Z","uid":279819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"843fa44aa6442c92b56c7c9df7a207cf01df0d5b","tid":1611813,"uid":279819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191002/60106958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60106958&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdEPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=7a3150f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60106958&h=7031b21a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191002/60106958</a><br />\n<br />\n警務處處長盧偉聰昨晚於記者會上表示，警方在油麻地、荃灣及黃大仙3個地點，都有警員使用警槍，總共開了6槍，包括荃灣向中五生開槍。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果讀者昨日在黃大仙龍翔道與沙田坳道交界，拍下警員開槍一幕，從讀者提供的片段所見，一批防暴警及便裝警員，在街頭拘捕兩名抗爭人士，當時場面混亂，其間有一名便裝警員首先拔槍，警員制服兩名抗爭人士便一同後退，有防暴警施放催淚彈掩護撤退，其間再有一名防暴警及一名便裝警員拔出佩槍，指向前面一批在遠處的抗爭人士，警員帶同被捕人士撤離期間，其中一名穿白色T恤便裝警員開了一槍。<br />\n讀者表示，看到一批警員突然衝出龍翔道，抗爭者四散逃走，警員制服兩人並按在地上，其後有警員拔槍指向抗爭人士，當時附近幾十米外都沒有人，之後警員在撤退期間無端開槍，聽到兩響槍聲，其中一下槍聲特別大，相信是實彈，另一下是催淚彈的聲響。"},{"pid":"285f8e760d0dd967f93327c89968e992f36fa174","tid":1611813,"uid":64816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:13:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"453cecca01a39aeb2d2c9844d7c2d38624105ba5","tid":1611813,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:55:00.000Z","msg":"核彈冇人推"},{"pid":"c8c62392f96a96bc7b60c993b529e30787cea4b2","tid":1611813,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:58:18.000Z","msg":"CLS!"},{"pid":"22423a94bcb4d13a1d404254654819c1688ec317","tid":1611813,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:00:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"215922637038aeb8e42a82609f31c4a89d84d4e7","tid":1611813,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:00:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府即將告你暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有全民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無&middot;限&middot;期</span>罷工罷課先可以救自己、救義士！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，今日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協，答應五大訴求為止！</span>"},{"pid":"9706460bcdf25696ef89343f372fabf6f4705671","tid":1611813,"uid":67303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:06:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbce9668e7de9fee669783586a281e99a1137409","tid":1611813,"uid":170160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:11:08.000Z","msg":"我覺呢個仲嚴重，因為近距離已冇實胰即時危險，而示威者亦已逃跑走避中，離遠不斷開實彈槍，係存心當狩獵殺人，射唔中人只係好彩 !  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5022d639976a240e1b5c36b6d9a13ae34ba41167","tid":1611813,"uid":307857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:13:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-siz